{
  "stem": "11904.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, yes, of course.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They bought a bicycle for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were older people already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said-- before-- like, every Sunday, it was-- the way it was done there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Every Sunday, the farmers or the vendors used to come into their house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had a beautiful house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he had an office.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was sitting there in his office.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the vendors would come in and they would sell them this, or sell him so many, so many, so many.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, the day before they had to ship them to take them to the yard-- you had to go out to all the farmers and give them the information-- when they should come, where, all those things.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because they haven't-- didn't have any phones.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, this couple actually had a phone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the others didn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I used to go on that bike, drive around to all those places, and tell them what to do.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And people treated me wonderful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was really, really, really well, all those buyers-- [NON-ENGLISH], they call them, the farmers in Austria.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They used to feed me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They used to give me things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the day of the-- of the transport, the man that I'm talking about, their name I know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was Wurzinger-- Frau and Herr Wurzinger.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- he had-- he would-- his right arm, it was amputated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or he lost it, I think, in a drunken brawl.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because he was a drinker.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so he didn't have a right arm, and couldn't write.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I had to go with him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As the cattle was weighed, they'd call out the pounds and all those things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I had to write it in for him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I went with him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was my sort of official job.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
